", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2019813: Fix off-by-one in imported memory index.  a=pascalc\n\nAfter rearranging the import process for compact imports, the\nimportIndex property assigned to memories became off by one.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D285313\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D285525\n", "files": ["js/src/jit-test/tests/wasm/builtin-modules/bug2019813.js", "js/src/wasm/WasmValidate.cpp"], "git_node": "9a0af7a47857690eb43f04ab324c9a7186c9ae47", "git_parents": ["b10f6eb5d290fec7a0e4c25edfe483c505e88800"], "node": "63db12afff64f1c54d1c56dea52f6403e976f0e1", "parents": ["5e5cc2b51cfe0734c598d69cf411ba8879a848be"], "tags": []}], "date": 1772525252, "git_changesets": ["9a0af7a47857690eb43f04ab324c9a7186c9ae47"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "24858": {"changesets": [{"author": "Andr\u00e9 Bargull \u003candre.bargull@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2018592: Combine code paths in ResizableArrayBufferObject::copy.  a=pascalc\n\nThis code path is only used for small buffers, so let's simplify it a bit.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D284448\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D285446\n", "files": ["js/src/vm/ArrayBufferObject.cpp"], "git_node": "85fe8afba094e3ed547a927924775c1fc0a3d68b", "git_parents": ["9a0af7a47857690eb43f04ab324c9a7186c9ae47"], "node": "5170896089ff241be411b3a0242286a487c2acec", "parents": ["63db12afff64f1c54d1c56dea52f6403e976f0e1"], "tags": []}], "date": 1772525366, "git_changesets": ["85fe8afba094e3ed547a927924775c1fc0a3d68b"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "24859": {"changesets": [{"author": "Finn Terdal \u003cfterdal@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2019296-02-25 - Fix default font option disappears  a=pascalc\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D284897\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D285586\n", "