Original Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D283698\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D285844\n", "files": ["browser/components/ipprotection/content/ipprotection-status-card.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/browser/browser_ipprotection_status_card.js"], "git_node": "99e5e0995118bc74180df5e053a5365faba387e4", "git_parents": ["711b1c72151fe058d0b0486e993ddc1060899b4e"], "node": "4268f49427833a21eaaf54d8ed7aee904dbf00ac", "parents": ["4c3677b5e662cfe89586236295199a10f1436a50"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Sebastian Streich \u003csstreich@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2017603 - Create a new Guardian Client when doing a re-init  a=pascalc\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D283881\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D285845\n", "files": ["browser/components/ipprotection/IPProtectionService.sys.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/browser/browser_ipprotection_status_box.js", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/browser/head.js", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/xpcshell/head.js", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/xpcshell/test_IPProtectionService.js"], "git_node": "099fb3571dc0bdac9d89c5f062bbdbd81e7ec0d2", "git_parents": ["99e5e0995118bc74180df5e053a5365faba387e4"], "node": "c1f79417e6c445c38d3c981a3d0546d4a35b11d7", "parents": ["4268f49427833a21eaaf54d8ed7aee904dbf00ac"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Fred Chasen \u003cfchasen@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2017756 - Update the IPPProxyManager error flow.  a=pascalc\n\nUpdates to the error handling and states for the proxy:\n- `ERROR` state for the proxy is limited to when the state was `ACTIVE`.\n- State will remain `ERROR` and hold requests until `stop()` is called.\n- Failures during activating the proxy reset the proxy state to the previous one.\n- Proxy errors all have constants for their messages.\n\nUpdates to how errors show in the UI:\n- Failures starting the proxy, such as network failures, are only shown in the panel the attempt to start was in.\n- When showing an error screen, a panel updates the state of the toolbar button in its window.\n- Toolbar button state is reset when the panel is opened or closed to match the panel's state.\n- Error updates triggered by the proxy ERROR state still show on all window toolbars.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D284329\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D285846\n", "files": ["browser/components/ipprotection/IPPProxyManager.sys.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/IPProtection.sys.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/IPProtectionPanel.sys.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/IPProtectionToolbarButton.sys.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/content/ipprotection-constants.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/docs/StateMachine.rst", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/browser/browser_IPProtectionService.js", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/browser/browser_ipprotection_network_error.js", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/browser/browser_ipprotection_panel.js", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/xpcshell/test_IPProxyManager.js"], "git_node": "78ccd84815c25531c869178901cb42857eb33c7d", "git_parents": ["099fb3571dc0bdac9d89c5f062bbdbd81e7ec0d2"], "node": "c7f681153ff7d7b392c5bdba01a82dfe00c6d4ce", "parents": ["c1f79417e6c445c38d3c981a3d0546d4a35b11d7"], "tags": []}], "date": 1772603611, "git_changesets": ["c50f41dd439622842b7ef43329c234d2abbf0b9b", "711b1c72151fe058d0b0486e993ddc1060899b4e", "99e5e0995118bc74180df5e053a5365faba387e4", "099fb3571dc0bdac9d89c5f062bbdbd81e7ec0d2", "78ccd84815c25531c869178901cb42857eb33c7d"], "user": "pchevrel@mozilla.com"}, "24876": {"changesets": [{"author": "Release Engineering Landoscript \u003crelease+landoscript@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No Bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets r=release a=l10n-bump\n\nach -\u00